title: [Saewehna Jungle, Cave]
description: Lapping effortlessly at the moss and algae enshrouded walls of the enclosure, the murky water ripples lazily in ebbs and surges.  Dusky shadows within the cave enhance the absolute darkness of the night outside, and the hushed music of nocturnal creatures accompanies the melodic sounds of the falls in the background.

Lapping effortlessly at the moss and algae enshrouded walls of the enclosure, the vividly hued water ripples lazily in ebbs and surges.  The dusky shadows of the cave afford a buffer to the sun, and the hushed music of the falls provides a soothing background.
room.location: the environs of the Saewehna Lagoon
